-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-8steNbbRJobsfitloeA_6-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-8steNbbRJobsfitloeA_6-4"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-8steNbbRJobsfitloeA_6-5"><sup><i><b>f</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation web">Dyson, Michael Eric (2001-12-11). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://docs.newsbank.com/openurl?ctx_ver=z39.88-2004&amp;rft_id=info:sid/iw.newsbank.com:NewsBank:CSTB&amp;rft_val_format=info:ofi/fmt:kev:mtx:ctx&amp;rft_dat=0F07FAAF0BEBA83F&amp;svc_dat=InfoWeb:aggregated5&amp;req_dat=AA98CDC331574F0ABEAFF732B33DC0B2">"8 steps to equality - New book by Rep. Jackson offers bold strategy for improving the lives of everyday Americans"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Chicago_Sun-Times" title="Chicago Sun-Times">Chicago Sun-Times</a></i>. Newsbank<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2008-05-23</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AA+More+Perfect+Union%3A+Advancing+New+American+Rights&amp;rft.atitle=8+steps+to+equality+-+New+book+by+Rep.+Jackson+offers+bold+strategy+for+improving+the+lives+of+everyday+Americans&amp;rft.au=Dyson%2C+Michael+Eric&amp;rft.date=2001-12-11&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Chicago+Sun-Times&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.newsbank.com%2Fopenurl%3Fctx_ver%3Dz39.88-2004%26rft_id%3Dinfo%3Asid%2Fiw.newsbank.com%3ANewsBank%3ACSTB%26rft_val_format%3Dinfo%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Actx%26rft_dat%3D0F07FAAF0BEBA83F%26svc_dat%3DInfoWeb%3Aaggregated5%26req_dat%3DAA98CDC331574F0ABEAFF732B33DC0B2&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>\n<li id="cite_note-RJkpbwcfC-7"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-RJkpbwcfC_7-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-RJkpbwcfC_7-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-RJkpbwcfC_7-